"(Bd, Jel.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mano SaAma", "text_ar": "مَنْ صَامَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ramaDAna A_iymaAnFA waA@HotisaAbFA", "text_ar": "رَمَضانَ اـِيمَانًا وَا@حْتِسَابًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in a trad.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Whoso fasteth during Ramadán, believing"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in God and his Apostle,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "reckoning upon a reward,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "seeking a reward"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "from God. (Mgh, * TA.) You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHtsb bika*aA A^ajorFA Einoda A@ll~`hi", "text_ar": "احتسب بِكَذَا اَجْرًا عِنْدَ ا@للّٰهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He reckoned upon obtaining,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he sought,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "by such a thing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "such an action, a reward from God:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(PS:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he prepared,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "provided, such a thing, seeking thereby a reward from God."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHtsb Einoda A@ll~`hi xayorFA", "text_ar": "احتسب عِنْدَ ا@للّٰهِ خَيْرًا"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He prepared,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "provided, in store for himself, good,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a reward,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with God."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, Mgh.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHtsb AlA^ajora EalaY A@ll~`hi", "text_ar": "احتسب الاَجْرَ عَلَى ا@للّٰهِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He laid up for himself, in store, the reward, with God, not hoping for the reward of the present life;"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AiHotisaAbu AlA^ajori", "text_ar": "اِحْتِسَابُ الاَجْرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "relating only to an action done for the sake of God. (Msb.) [Hence,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHtsb waladahu", "text_ar": "احتسب وَلَدَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (A, Mgh,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A@bonahu", "text_ar": "ا@بْنَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Msb,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A@bonFA", "text_ar": "ا@بْنًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bnotFA", "text_ar": "بنْتًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, K, *) is said when one has lost by death an adult child or son or daughter; (S, A, Mgh, Msb, K;) meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He prepared,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "provided, in store for himself, a reward, by his patience on the occasion of his being afflicted and tried by the death of his adult child:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh, * TA:) when a man has lost by death a child not arrived at the age of puberty, you say of him,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AifotaraTahu", "text_ar": "اِفْتَرَطَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S, A, Msb, K.) [Hence also,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHtsb", "text_ar": "احتسب"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eamalahu", "text_ar": "عَمَلَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He reckoned upon,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "prepared for himself, a reward by his deed:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he did his deed seeking a reward from God in the world to come."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(L, TA.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AiHotasabotu baAl$~aYo'i", "text_ar": "اِحْتَسَبْتُ بَالشَّىْءِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I included the thing in a numbering,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "reckoning;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "made account of it; accounted it a matter of importance."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fulaAnN laA yuHotasabu", "text_ar": "فُلَانٌ لَا يُحْتَسَبُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lA yHtsb bahi", "text_ar": "لا يحتسب بَهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one is made no account of; is not esteemed,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "regarded, as of any account,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "importance."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, TA.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AiHotasabotu Einodahu", "text_ar": "اِحْتَسَبْتُ عِنْدَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aikotafayotu", "text_ar": "اِكْتَفَيْتُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, sufficed,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "contented, thereat,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "at his abode"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A, TA.) [And IbrD thinks that the verb has the same signification in the phrase"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AiHotasabotu Ealayohi biAlmaAli", "text_ar": "اِحْتَسَبْتُ عَلَيْهِ بِالمَالِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", quoted in the TA from the A; holding"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Elyh", "text_ar": "عليه"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "to be here used in the sense of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eanohu", "text_ar": "عَنْهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; so that the meaning is"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, sufficed, so as to have no need of him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it, by the property:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "but I doubt whether this phrase be correctly transcribed.] ―         -b4-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHtsb", "text_ar": "احتسب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also signifies"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AinotahaY", "text_ar": "اِنْتَهَى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He abstained,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "desisted;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "app. as one sufficed, or contented]. (K.) ―         -b5-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHtsb Ealayohi ka*aA", "text_ar": "احتسب عَلَيْهِ كَذَا"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He disapproved and disallowed his doing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "having done, such a"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 566}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thing;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K; *) namely, a foul deed: (TA:) whence the appellation ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "muHotasibN", "text_ar": "مُحْتَسِبٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (K.) And accord. to some,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHtsb A@ll~`ha Ealayohi", "text_ar": "احتسب ا@للّٰهَ عَلَيْهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He said, May God take,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "execute, vengeance upon him;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "punish him;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "for his evil deeds. (Har p. 371. [See"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HasiybN", "text_ar": "حَسِيبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".]) [In the present day,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHtsb Ealayohi", "text_ar": "احتسب عَلَيْهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is used as meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He prayed for aid against him by saying,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HasobunaA A@ll~`hu", "text_ar": "حَسْبُنَا ا@للّٰهُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "God is,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "will be, sufficient for us."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] ―         -b6-  You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHtsb fulaAnFA", "text_ar": "احتسب فُلَانًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHtsb maA Einodahu", "text_ar": "احتسب مَا عِنْدَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (A,) meaning (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He endeavoured to learn what such a one had"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in his mind,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in his possession"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A, K, * TA.) ―         -b7-  See also 4."}], "source_refs": ["S", "K", "PS", "A", "Mgh", "Msb", "TA"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}